Notes: Galyan's Div. III Holiday Tournament...SP advances to title game to face
Heidelberg, which beat Franklin 89-80 in OT...SP's Heuer scored career-high 23
points...SP led 20-15 with 12:50 left in first half and made eight of next
nine shots during 21-3 run over next six minutes...First meeting between teams
Game.Officials: Roger Marley,  Annie Timmons,  Tim Carr
